碧昂斯关于《Break My Soul》样本的诉讼被撤销https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-lawsuit-over-break-my-soul-sample-dropped-3782348?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=beyonce-lawsuit-over-break-my-soul-样本丢失Liberty DunworthFri, 09 Aug 2024 10:07:08 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopR&B https://www.nme.com/?p=3782348 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="碧昂丝在“RENAISSANCE WORLD TOUR”舞台上表演" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>今年年初的文件称，Da Showstoppaz 的 2022 年歌曲在她采样的一首流行歌曲中非法出现</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-lawsuit-over-break-my-soul-sample-dropped-3782348">碧昂丝因《Break My Soul》样本被删除而提起的诉讼</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="碧昂丝在“RENAISSANCE WORLD TOUR”舞台上表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>针对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂丝</a>的热门单曲“Break My Soul”提起的诉讼已被撤销。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beyonce-cowboy-carter-album-review-tracklist-lyrics-3611699">碧昂斯 - 《牛仔卡特》评论：国家重塑收获金币</a></strong></li></ul><p>该文件于 5 月首次披露，由新奥尔良一个名为 Da Showstoppaz 的团体提出，该团体<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-accused-of-copyright-infringement-on-break-my-soul-3758874">指控这位流行歌星侵犯了</a>她的热门单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beyonce-renaissance-review-tracklist-artwork-3278806">“Renaissance”</a>的版权。</p><p>该问题源于碧昂斯 2022 年歌曲《Big Freedia》的采样，乐队声称她非法使用了 2002 年歌曲“Release A Wiggle”中的歌词。</p><p>乐队成员泰莎·阿维 (Tessa Avie)、凯瓦·布尔乔亚 (Keva Bourgeois)、亨利·布拉格 (Henri Braggs) 和布莱恩·克拉克 (Brian Clark) 均向路易斯安那州联邦法院提起诉讼。在文件中，他们声称 Bey 采样了 Big Freedia 2014 年的歌曲“Explode”——然而，后者非法使用了自己歌曲中的“受版权保护的歌词、旋律和音乐编排”，使得“Break My Soul”中的这一功能非法。</p><p>除了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beyonce-cowboy-carter-album-review-tracklist-lyrics-3611699">“牛仔卡特”</a>歌手外，Big Freedia、索尼音乐、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jay-z">Jay-Z</a>等也被列为被告。</p><p>目前，已确认版权诉讼已被主动驳回。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/beyonce-break-my-soul-sample-lawsuit-dropped-1235076690/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《滚石》</em></a>报道，法庭文件中没有提及和解协议，这意味着该案很可能只是被撤销。该媒体还补充说，当被要求置评时，碧昂丝和 Da Showstoppaz 的代表均未做出回应。 </p><p><iframe title="碧昂丝 - BREAK MY SOUL（官方歌词视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yjki-9Pthh0?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在五月提交的文件中，投诉提请人们注意这首歌如何取得巨大成功，因为它在美国单曲排行榜上名列前茅，在 Bey 的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-renaissane-tour-tickets-2023-uk-europe-north-america-buy-tickets-3390499">“文艺复兴”巡演</a>中频繁播放，并出现在她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/beyonces-renaissance-movie-praised-in-first-reviews-made-for-the-big-screen-3549674">随附的有关现场表演的纪录片</a>中。</p><p> “太太。 Carter、Big Freedia、Parkwood、Sony 等公司通过《Explode》、《Break My Soul》、《Renaissance》专辑、《Renaissance 世界巡演》和《Renaissance: A Film by Beyoncé》获得了许多赞誉和丰厚利润，”它说。 “Da Showstoppaz 没有收到任何东西——没有任何认可、没有荣誉、没有任何形式的报酬。”</p><p>在诉讼中，新奥尔良乐队要求获得《Break My Soul》和《Explode》的版权并获得赔偿，以及未来曲目许可的版税。</p><p>鉴于 Beyoncé 已合法授权 Big Freedia 歌曲“Explode”的样本，因此对 Da Showstoppaz 的涉嫌侵权纯属意外。</p><p>自 2024 年初以来，Bey 因其乡村风格专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beyonce-cowboy-carter-album-review-tracklist-lyrics-3611699">“Cowboy Carter”</a>的巨大成功而登上了无数头条新闻。 </p><figure id="attachment_3612396" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3612396" style="width: 1200px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3612396" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/COWBOY-CARTER-MAIN-COVER-ART.jpeg" alt="" width="1200" height="1200" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/COWBOY-CARTER-MAIN-COVER-ART.jpeg 1200w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/COWBOY-CARTER-MAIN-COVER-ART-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/COWBOY-CARTER-MAIN-COVER-ART-400x400.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/COWBOY-CARTER-MAIN-COVER-ART-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/COWBOY-CARTER-MAIN-COVER-ART-696x696.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/COWBOY-CARTER-MAIN-COVER-ART-1068x1068.jpeg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3612396" class="wp-caption-text"> “牛仔卡特”——主要封面艺术。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>专辑问世后不久，它就创下了无数里程碑，包括凭借《Texas Hold &#39;Em》 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-becomes-first-black-woman-to-hit-number-one-on-us-country-chart-359055">成为第一位在美国乡村音乐排行榜上排名第一的黑人女性</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-becomes-first-black-woman-to-land-us-number-one-country-album-with-cowboy-carter-3614606">也是第一位在美国乡村专辑排行榜上排名第一的黑人女性</a>，并获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/michelle-obama-praises-beyonces-cowboy-carter-you-have-changed-the-game-once-again-3612514">米歇尔·奥巴马</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-mccartney-speaks-out-on-beyonces-fabulous-cover-of-blackbird-for-fighting-racial-tension-3613377">保罗·麦卡特尼</a>等知名人士的支持。</p><p>这位明星还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-beyonce-new-pony-up-remix-of-texas-hold-em-3613115">分享了《Texas Hold &#39;Em》的混音版</a>，并透露她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-used-original-beatles-blackbird-backing-track-for-cowboy-carter-version-with-paul-mccartneys-blessing-3613264">在封面中保留了 1968 年原版《Blackbird》的大部分原始背景音乐</a>。她还证实<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-thanks-stevie-wonder-for-playing-harmonica-on-jolene-cover-3612108">史蒂维·旺德在《Jolene》中演奏口琴</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-reveals-that-she-co-wrote-beyonces-riiverdance-on-cowboy-carter-3611049">RAYE 则被认为是一首《牛仔卡特》歌曲的共同创作者</a>。</p><p>最近，这位“单身女士”歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-celebrates-gymnast-simone-biles-historic-olympic-win-brilliance-it-doesnt-come-easy-3780502">在 2024 年巴黎奥运会上公开表达了对美国著名体操运动员西蒙·拜尔斯 (Simone Biles) 的支持</a>，并为<em>NBC 体育频道</em>录制了宣传视频，称赞她“鼓舞人心”且“才华横溢”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-lawsuit-over-break-my-soul-sample-dropped-3782348">碧昂丝因《Break My Soul》样本被删除而提起的诉讼</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
